data.description: This beautiful home is nestled on a spacious 0.57-acre lot in the desirable Walker Place neighborhood. The exterior boasts a recently replaced roof, and solar panels that can save you hundreds of dollars on monthly electricity payments! SOLAR PANELS WILL BE PAID BY SELLER AT CLOSING. The interior boasts an open-concept design, complete with a cozy fireplace in the living room that creates a warm and inviting ambiance. The well-appointed kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a breakfast area. Your primary suite has a spa-like ensuite bathroom complete with a dual vanity, relaxing tub, and separate shower. The split-bedroom floor plan offers enhanced privacy and separation between the primary suite and secondary bedrooms. Additionally, the attached 2 car garage provides secure parking and additional storage. Don’t miss the chance to make this your new home! Schedule a viewing today!
